content:
Hello, I'm trying to use torinox's snapshot command but I'm not sure if it's working? I can upload my profile to simplifier and see the snapshot there so I know my profile is valid as are the dependencies in the package. However, when I try the snapshot command via torinox it gives me an error. Screen-Shot-2019-06-27-at-9.47.02-AM.png

@Martijn Harthoorn
Hi @Natasha Singh , it looks like you are trying to generate a snapshot with torinox for FHIR R4 on a StructureDefinition for R3.

You can run the R3 (STU3) of Torinox side by side with the R4 version.
https://simplifier.net/downloads/torinox
Ah I see, thanks @Martijn Harthoorn . That worked
